sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant Server

    User->>Browser: Enters a new note and clicks "Save"
    Browser->>Server: HTTP POST request to /exampleapp/new_note_spa with note data (JSON)
    Server-->>Browser: Responds with success confirmation (201 Created or 200 OK)
    
    Browser->>Server: HTTP GET request to /exampleapp/data.json (to fetch updated notes)
    Server-->>Browser: Sends updated JSON data with the new note
    
    Browser->>User: Updates UI with the new note (without reloading the page)
